title: Planipapillus vittatus
text: Planipapillus vittatus is a species of <a href="velvet%20worm">velvet worm</a> in the <a href="Peripatopsidae">Peripatopsidae</a> <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a>. It is found in <a href="Victoria%2C%20Australia">Victoria</a>, <a href="Australia">Australia</a>.
